org.springframework.cloud.netflix.zuul

Annotation Type EnableZuulServer


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Import(value=ZuulServerMarkerConfiguration.class)
public @interface EnableZuulServer
    Set up the application to act as a generic Zuul server without any built-in reverse proxy features. The routes into the Zuul server can be configured through ZuulProperties (by default there are none).
    Author:
    Spencer Gibb, Biju Kunjummen
    See Also:
    to see how to get reverse proxy out of the box
